main.description: I am a web development engineer and I use react and vue.js to develop pages. This project is a resume template that can be used as the project home page or resume page
main.bio: I am an aspiring full-stack engineer with a passion for developing robust and user-friendly web applications. With expertise in React and Vue.js for front-end development, I also enjoy working with backend technologies such as Node.js and Express. I thrive in collaborative environments and am always eager to learn and grow. In my free time, I love exploring new technologies, contributing to open-source projects, and sharing my knowledge with the developer community.
main.contactmessage: Feel free to reach out to me for collaboration, project ideas, or any inquiries. I'm always excited to connect with fellow developers and tech enthusiasts. Let's create something amazing together!
